OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWidely hot and locally very
OL,6,Fhot, especially inland, and also
OL,7,Ffeeling humid. Largely sunny with
OL,8,Flight winds, which will keep coastal
OL,9,Fareas cooler and fresher.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDespite largely clear skies
OL,12,Fmany places will have another warm or
OL,13,Fvery warm night, especially in large
OL,14,Ftowns and cities, with the humid
OL,15,Fconditions persisting.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
